<li><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Thailand.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Thailand.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a9/Flag_of_Thailand.svg/22px-Flag_of_Thailand.svg.png" width="22" height="15" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Thailand" title="Thailand">Thailand</a>: M4A1s sold as part of a 2006 <a href="/wiki/Foreign_Military_Sales" title="Foreign Military Sales">Foreign Military Sales</a> package.<sup id="cite_ref-Guns_2006_15-2" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Guns_2006-15" title=""><span>[</span>16<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
